WEBVTT

00:00:00.769 --> 00:00:04.215
I remember one morning
when I was in the third grade,

00:00:04.239 --> 00:00:08.870
my mom sent me to school
with a Ghanaian staple dish called "fufu."

00:00:08.894 --> 00:00:10.451
(Laughter)

00:00:10.475 --> 00:00:14.690
Fufu is this white ball of starch
made of cassava,

00:00:14.714 --> 00:00:19.079
and it's served with light soup,
which is a dark orange color,

00:00:19.103 --> 00:00:21.337
and contains chicken and/or beef.

00:00:21.859 --> 00:00:23.908
It's a savory, flavorful dish

00:00:23.932 --> 00:00:27.155
that my mom thought
would keep me warm on a cold day.

